data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on a sprawling 2.5-acre property, where the perfect blend of comfort, space & natural beauty awaits. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by the sight of an extra-large detached 2 car garage/workshop. Whether you're a DIY enthusiast or simply need ample storage space, this garage is sure to impress. Privacy is paramount, thanks to the new privacy fence that encircles the property. You'll enjoy a sense of seclusion & security, making this space truly your own. For those with an equestrian inclination, this property is thoughtfully zoned for horses. Step inside the home & you'll discover a well-designed layout with 3 main level bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, ensuring convenience, accessibility & functionality. Ascend a spiral staircase to reach the second-story loft adorned with hardwood flooring & an iron railing. This versatile space can be tailored to your preferences, whether you envision it as a cozy reading nook, an inspiring home office, or a tranquil retreat. The main level encompasses both a living room & a family room, ensuring ample space for relaxation & entertainment. The family room features a gas fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings when you want to create a warm & inviting atmosphere. Entertain to your heart's content in the game area, complete with a bar where you can serve up drinks & snacks to friends & family. This room promises endless fun & memories to cherish. The finished basement offers the potential for further customization, allowing you to create additional living space or storage solutions to suit your needs. If you're a pet lover or simply enjoy soaking up the sunshine, the dog room/enclosed sunroom is a delightful feature. Enjoy the great outdoors from the comfort of this space, no matter the weather. Lastly, don't forget to savor the stunning mountain views that surround the property. Welcome to your new haven, where every day feels like a retreat in the heart of nature's beauty.
